OL,5,G0300 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe competition kicks off at North
OL,7,     FBridge Street B&B in Hawick, where
OL,8,     FEileen Walsh and Emanuel Forte's
OL,9,     Fpurple-themed rooms cause quite a
OL,10,     Freaction among their guests.
OL,11,G0325 Four in a Bed
OL,12,     FAt The Golden Fleece in Cumbria,
OL,13,     FSylvia Spark and Robert Cowan aim
OL,14,     Fto please with some local fare at
OL,15,     Fbreakfast. But the plates swim in
OL,16,     Fgrease and the eggs are hard.
