OL,12,G0510 Couples Come Dine with Me
OL,13,     FEssex and east London. Spencer and
OL,14,     FSara serve a simple Jewish feast.
OL,15,     FLauren and Jack's menu reflects
OL,16,     Ftheir South African and Burmese
OL,17,     Fheritage. Paul and Ed's food
OL,18,     Fchallenges a picky palate.
